               <div className="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
               Deep Learning
            </h4>
            <p className="text-sm text-slate-500">Gemini 3 Flash provides unmatched accuracy in detecting complex table hierarchies.</p>
          </div>
          <div className="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
